Frequently asked questions

Can't find the answer you're looking for? Contact our support team.

How quickly can I expect a response?
We strive to respond to all inquiries within 24 hours during business days. For urgent matters, please mention this in your message subject.
Do you offer demos of the platform?
Yes! You can schedule a personal demo with one of our product specialists. They'll walk you through all the features and answer any questions specific to your use case.
I'm having trouble with my account. What should I do?
For account-related issues, please email support@venturehive.com with your username and a detailed description of the problem. Our technical team will assist you promptly.
Can I request a feature that's not currently available?
Absolutely! We love hearing feature suggestions from our users. Please use the contact form to submit your ideas, and our product team will review them for future updates.
